Primer3.pm development
====================

HOW TO BUILD

1. Make sure the necessary C code is in p3ccode/. 
   Usually during development you can you the
   getcode.pl in this directory:

   perl getcode.pl

2. make clean
   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test


*** The makefiles do not track all dependencies.
If you are developing in this directory, always start
with

   make clean


